@OR13 The last line of the readme currently reads

> Command line usage requires that you have the necessary software installed. [See the instructions](https://github.com/martinthomson/i-d-template/blob/main/doc/SETUP.md).

The linked instructions appear to only be for *nix-like operating systems (no Windows). Should we import those into this repo, or somehow make this line stand out more?

@brownoxford I just tried to run the commands in the readme and they failed on macOS.... they worked for me before (when we used docker).

I need the ability to preview changes locally to contribute.

All commands needed should be documented in the README.
